 He knows what it takes to create technology ideas,

00:51.920 --> 00:56.280
 designs, products and companies that revolutionize life

00:56.280 --> 00:59.120
 for huge numbers of people in the world.

00:59.120 --> 01:02.480
 So it truly is an honor and pleasure to sit down

01:02.480 --> 01:05.280
 with Tony for a time and look back at one heck

01:05.280 --> 01:06.520
 of an amazing life.

